0:00:00.080,0:00:02.080
Pane mukadzi uko; sezvandiri kutaura izvozvi;

0:00:02.260,0:00:05.200
Akagadzirira kutarisa murume wake waakasiyana naye.

0:00:05.200,0:00:07.920
Akarasikirwa nomurume wake kwemwedzi yakati ikozvino.

0:00:08.060,0:00:10.860
Mweya wake unoti, 'Ndiri kuzodana murume wangu,

0:00:10.900,0:00:14.620
Ndiri kuzotsvaka murume wangu 'ndoti, Ndapota, chero zvakaitika,' Ndine urombo zvikuru '.

0:00:14.680,0:00:15.340
Ari uko!

0:00:15.340,0:00:17.760
Mukadzi wacho anoda kuyananisa zvino.

0:00:17.900,0:00:19.840
Ndinoziva kuti murume wako akakugumbura.

0:00:19.840,0:00:21.420
Asi iwe unoda chaizvo kuyananisa.

0:00:21.480,0:00:25.900
Akati, iye anoda kuuya nomurume uyu pano kuti azive mafungiro a Mwari.

0:00:25.900,0:00:26.940
Mukadzi wacho ariko uko.

0:00:26.940,0:00:28.800
Iwe wakaisa ketani pamutsipa wako.

0:00:28.800,0:00:30.420
Uyai! iye ari uko.

0:00:37.100,0:00:39.660
Usanetseke! Ndapota ndinoda kuonana naye

0:00:39.660,0:00:40.580
Muregei iye, andimirire.

0:00:41.400,0:00:45.600
Simbiso ye Uporofita

0:00:46.680,0:00:49.660
Zita rangu ndi Jane Udensi

0:00:49.700,0:00:53.300
Ini ndinobva ku Anambra state, Nigeria

0:00:53.580,0:00:56.600
Munhu wa Mwari akati, pane mukadzi pano,

0:00:56.620,0:01:01.640
uye akanongedza ruoko rwake kurutivi, rwandaive ndigere.

0:01:01.740,0:01:07.280
Akati, 'pane mukadzi uko, murume wake akamusiya kwemwedzi yakati zvino,

0:01:07.380,0:01:11.060
uye iye akagadzirira kuyananisana nemurume wake, asi kwakanga kusina nzira.

0:01:11.180,0:01:16.000
Akataura zvakare kuti mukadzi akaisa nekiresi pamutsipa wake.

0:01:16.280,0:01:18.160
Ndinosimbisa kuti ichokwadi.

0:01:18.240,0:01:21.120
Iwe unogona kusimbisa sei uporofita uhwu kuva hwechokwadi?

0:01:21.120,0:01:27.740
Ndinotsigira kuti ndezve chokwadi nokuti kwemwedzi yakati ikozvino, murume wangu akandisiya.

0:01:27.740,0:01:31.660
Takanga tichi popotedzana uye kurwisana ndokubva andisiya,

0:01:31.660,0:01:35.840
nekuda kwe kushaya mbereko, hatina vana kubvira patakaroorana.

0:01:35.900,0:01:39.000
Zvakakanganisa imba yangu nokuti hakuna rugare;

0:01:39.040,0:01:41.960
taigara tichirwisana ne kupopotedzana nguva dzose.

0:01:42.020,0:01:47.740
Akandirongedzesa iye ndokuroora mumwe mukadzi

0:01:47.760,0:01:50.940
uye akandikumbira kuti ndiende kune mumwe murume.

0:01:51.280,0:01:53.940
Pakanga pasina rugare, pasina mufaro, pasina rudo.

0:01:53.940,0:02:04.020
Mumwedzi miviri yapfuura, akakanda zvinhu zvangu panze ndokutora zvimwe zvacho.

0:02:04.200,0:02:09.620
Handina kuita chero chinhu; akandirova ndokukanda zvinhu zvangu kunze.

0:02:09.700,0:02:12.380
Ndinosimbisa uporofita kuti ichokwadi.

0:02:12.780,0:02:15.380
Iye zvino iwe wakagamuchira huporofita;

0:02:15.400,0:02:21.080
uho Mwari wa Masimba Ose, akaunza budiriro, yananiso uye kuporeswa muupenyu hwako.

0:02:21.300,0:02:24.440
Hungu ndinotenda, nokuti kubva munhu wa Mwari akandidana,

0:02:24.480,0:02:27.340
Ndinoziva kuti dambudziko rangu rapera.

0:02:27.660,0:02:32.640
Ameni, tinotenda Jesu Kristu nokuda kweuporofita hwakanaka hwawagamuchira nhasi.

0:02:32.640,0:02:35.280
Nhasi ndiro zuva rako dzvene rokusangana na Jesu Kristu.

0:02:35.280,0:02:39.660
Uye isu tinotenda kuti nzira yako yakazarurwa.

0:02:39.660,0:02:43.660
Tinoda kukukurudzira, kuti utore Shoko ra Mwari se nhungamiro ye hupenyu hwako,

0:02:43.660,0:02:48.700
kuitira kuti uchengetedze kuporeswa kwakanakisa kwaucha gamuchira, uye yananiso muzita ra Jesu.

0:02:49.640,0:02:50.300
Ameni

0:02:54.060,0:02:59.080
Zita rangu ndi Jane Udensi, ini ndinobva ku Anambra state, Nigeria.

0:02:59.760,0:03:03.380
Svondo yapfuura munhu wa Mwari akaprofita kuti, pane mukadzi pano;

0:03:03.380,0:03:09.960
uyo akanga asiya murume wake kwemwedzi inopfuura miviri ikozvino,

0:03:10.080,0:03:16.120
uye mukadzi wacho akapfeka nekiresi uyezve mukadzi wacho anoda kuyananisana nemurume wake.

0:03:16.180,0:03:19.900
Asi murume akaramba. Ipapo ndakabuda.

0:03:20.700,0:03:26.760
Akandidzinga, nokuti kubvira patakaroorana hapana vana.

0:03:26.760,0:03:28.140
uye hapana rudo.

0:03:28.140,0:03:34.220
Akataura zvakare kuti ndakanga ndine murume we mumweya, uyo akanga achimutambudza mukurota kwake.

0:03:34.220,0:03:38.580
Akataura kuti ndaiva ogbanje - svikiro uye ndaiita kuti arware.

0:03:38.880,0:03:43.800
Ndinofunga zvine musoro ndezve kuti, tinofanira kunzwa kubva kune mukoma wedu.

0:03:44.100,0:03:47.280
Zita rangu ndi Ogochukwu Udensi, ndakabva ku Anambra state, Nigeria.

0:03:49.480,0:04:02.240
Ichokwadi kuti ndakadzinga mudzimai wangu nokuti kubvira patakaroorana hakuna mwana, hapana rudo.

0:04:02.460,0:04:12.880
Nokuti mudzimai wangu aiva nemurume we mumweya ainditambudza muhope dzangu.

0:04:13.180,0:04:16.620
Aizotakura pfuti, kana banga ondidzingirira.

0:04:16.920,0:04:19.100
Akauya panyama here?

0:04:19.280,0:04:21.280
Kwete, muhope, Munhu wa Mwari.

0:04:21.500,0:04:25.360
Sei! tiudze kuti akauya sei muchiroto?

0:04:25.680,0:04:32.240
Aizotakura pfuti, dzimwe nguva aitakura banga uye ini ndaizomhanya.

0:04:32.300,0:04:37.640
Murume we mumweya akafanana nomudzimai wangu, ainditevera nepfuti.

0:04:37.660,0:04:42.420
Wakazviziva sei, kuti mudzimai wako ndiye aiyichinja kuve murume we mumweya?

0:04:42.480,0:04:47.220
Nokuti, ndaigona kumuona chiso chake.

0:04:51.820,0:04:54.940
Ndicho chikonzero, iwe wakamudzingira kunze?

0:04:54.980,0:04:56.980
Hungu, ichokwadi munhu wa Mwari.

0:04:57.160,0:05:04.120
Akataura kuti chikonzero akadzinga mukadzi wake. Wanano yakaparara

0:05:04.160,0:05:12.760
nokuti aigara achiona mukadzi uyu muchiroto achiuya kuzomurwisa nepfuti, ane zvombo,

0:05:12.760,0:05:16.280
uye nguva dzose azviwana achimhanya.

0:05:17.000,0:05:20.900
Muhupenyu chaihwo, mudzimai wako aigara achikutevera here?

0:05:21.260,0:05:22.100
Kwete

0:05:22.320,0:05:27.420
Mudzimai wako haagoni kukufarira iwe panyama, saka sei iwe uri kutiza muhope?

0:05:27.460,0:05:30.040
Uye iwe unoziva mudzimai wako, sei usingakwanisi kumumirira?

0:05:30.040,0:05:31.760
Nokuti aida kundiuraya.

0:05:31.980,0:05:34.020
Ndokusaka ndakatiza.

0:05:34.440,0:05:37.360
Vose vari vaviri vanoda dzikinuro.

0:05:37.360,0:05:46.520
Uye mushure medzikinuro yake iye achazoziva kuti, iye atori muvengi kunyanya kupfuura zvaari shamwari kumudzimai wake.

0:05:46.540,0:05:50.100
Uye mudzimaiwo zvakare muvengi kupfuura shamwari.

0:05:50.220,0:05:51.340
Unonditeerera here?

0:05:51.500,0:05:52.660
Ndichadzokorora zvakare.

0:05:52.720,0:05:59.540
Iwe uri muvengi kunyanya kupfuura zvauri shamwari kumudzimai wako, uye mudzimai wako muvengi kunyanya, kupfuura zvaari shamwari yako.

0:05:59.860,0:06:02.500
Saka ndiani muroyi, ndiani muuki?

0:06:04.900,0:06:12.380
Kana mudzimai ari muroyi, pachake iye muuki.

0:06:12.380,0:06:18.460
Ndapota muudzei kuti: Kana mudzimai ari muroyi zvechokwadi, iye pachake muuki.

0:06:18.640,0:06:21.380
Ndizvozvo zvose, vaviri vavo vanoda kununurwa.

0:06:21.380,0:06:22.140
Mazvita

0:06:22.140,0:06:27.280
Ivo murume nemudzimai. Iyi iwanano inobva kuna Mwari.

0:06:30.340,0:06:36.140
Tinovimba kuti wakurudzirwa nevhidhiyo yawabva mukuona.

0:06:36.300,0:06:42.540
Tinya apa kuti unyorese kupupurira zvakawanda pamusoro pesimba ra Mwari pabasa munguva yatiri nhasi

0:06:42.700,0:06:49.340
kuti ugare uri pamusoro pezvichagoburwa zvehuporofita,dzikinuro, mharidzo nezvapupu

